      "text": "The quotation here, plus the phrase \"when quined,\" indirectly refers to the entire sentence. The importance of this fact is that the remainder of the sentence, the phrase \"makes quite a statement,\" can now make a statement about the sentence as a whole. If we had used a pronoun for this, we could have written something like \"this sentence makes quite a statement.\""
